subtitleNullable: Original csv files of the first case study's travel information for Cyclistic
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is the original version of the data required to complete Case Study 1 of the Google Data Analytics Capstone course, based on a fictitious bike-sharing firm in Chicago called Cyclistic.
The dataset contains trip information in 12 months from 2022/03 to 2023/02 of the database available on this [website](https://divvy-tripdata.s3.amazonaws.com/index.html).
The data has been made available by Motivate International Inc. under this [license](https://ride.divvybikes.com/data-license-agreement).
